tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia</span><br>  Posts: 1161<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/21/02 2:06:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=116.topic>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou3.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Love is for the Weak.</span><hr size=1> I tire of this silly and useless Emotion. Love does not power hate. Light does not power darkness.  Love is weakness, and weakness is in love.<br>
<br>
One that has never known love is powerful. Without that worthless Emotion slowing him down, splitting his heart and soul which he should be devoting in his faith, he wastes it on some pathetic other Male or Woman, whichever the case. Its a waste of effort and time.<br>
<br>
Their is one thing now that gets me up and puts me to sleep, daily. That is my hate. My Constant reminder that I will destroy the Lightbringers, I will stand above and kill them all.<br>
<br>
The 'Mighty' Gore has been destroyed. Why? Because pathetically, he fell in love. No longer was his heart devoted to Bloodshed and Battles, now devoted to Misha, some little blue elf stringing the poor fool along. His Doll as it were was split and became dependent on Misha to keep him standing.<br>
And you know what happened? Such stong trust left him reeling. Ogarth killed him. And soon enought, his own love destroyed him. <br>
<br>
Love destroyed others as well, Gore is not the only one to fall, but he's the strongest pure fighter to fall to its whims.<br>
<br>
An perfect example, Mr Demiath. Here, a Tier'dal Priest.. filled with the Perfect Hate of the Father! His hate was astounding..<br>
Before he met those Harlots of love, Do I really need to say their names? You know who I am talking about, and no, they are not the only ones, but they are a sparkling example.<br>
<br>
Roose twisted and destroyed that Hatred sprit that Demiath was. Demiath was a Great man untill he ran into her. I daily tried to ressurect him as Roose destroyed one of the Fathers Creations, I could hear his true sprit yearning to be free of this pathetic love. But it was not to be, she had him.<br>
<br>
In the end, he became a Tier'dal Priest of love. How Pathetic. After he had made his final Transgression, I had no choice but fight and make an example of him. We broke even in battles.<br>
<br>
But in the end, it was her that would deal the final blow. She shattered his worthless love, and kicked him to the side when she was finished with him. How foolish of you Demiath, falling in love with that trash.<br>
<br>
Where did becomming a Priest of Love get Demiath? Nothing but wasted time he could of put to good use destroying the creations of Tunare. He was not strong enought to put those people to good use as I did in the past, and they almost destroyed him.<br>
<br>
If you must know, I believe he has recovered and is doing fine, I think he is with the Lightbringers, but I am not sure, a flaw that will never becorrected thanks to love.<br>
<br>
Juonar and Celiesta.. Ahh, a star crossed pair. One Tier'dal Knight, and one Tier'dal Priestess, both in the way of the Father, and both in Love. Their love was boundless, first started by lust, but Celiesta fell weak to it, as did Juonar. They became closer, their love forcing the two to lean on one other just to stand.<br>
Then, Celiesta was ripped away. A Family arrangement. Celiesta was to marry another.<br>
<br>
Now, Both Celiesta and Juonar are dead. So much potental for these two to do the Fathers work, wasted. Why?<br>
Because of love.<br>
<br>
But I stand here as your example. I have had a woman's love, almost my Entire life untill lately. From Genashai to Sarhea to Kallee to Vivienne and Vienna to Citrellis, and what has that love done to make me stronger?! Not a thing!<br>
Only two of these women I did not love. But it is not their fault, nono. They have no control over it, its the fault of Love itself~! I am lucky however. I faught back against love. I am not proud of how I had to do it, Love tried to box me in and I had to bring out everything I had just to break even and have a chance at survival.<br>
<br>
Love is caring deeply. Love is pretty, roses and blue skies.. the Bird flies over the skies singing a song of Peace and Harmony.<br>
<br>
I hate peace and harmony. These Unions of Love called &quot;Marriages&quot; shall end. The Father deems it so, for with his Hate, I have all I need. I need not this thing called a Woman's love, I am stronger without it.<br>
<br>
I'm in my 52nd level of power. The Neutralic powers I seek to fight are still way above me, and they shall continue to grow as the Planes of Power are revieled and our bodies are able to raise to new levels of power. Why am I so weakened, only now being able to crawl out of the Hole I was put in and stand above?<br>
<br>
Because of Love! Their worthless love chipped away at what I was, what I should of been by now. Some tired to use me, some tried to whore me. Some tried to love me. Does it matter? No. Its all love, and it all should be destroyed. Its the blessings of a worthless lesser Priestess, and it shall be crushed just like the Many Paladins under my Heel of Hatred(R).<br>
<br>
I point to you, Young Necromancer. Young ShadowKnight, Young Follower of The Father, follower of Hate. Bewear these worthless blessings, the Blessings of love. Be weary of it, do not falter like the Pathetic Paladin, droping himself and everything for the love of a another who will just shatter him in the end. Stand tall and above it, your hate.. Hate the very essence of it. Hate all that Love stands for. This will strenghten your hate even further, and you will become stronger with it.<br>
<br>
Take your pleasures if you need be. But that is all. Fall in love and lose all that you stand for.<br>
<br>
For I stand before you now, My sprit torn and beaten, battered throught a life of the Torments of Love. It cuts deeper then any blade, it tears harder then any claw, and destroys faster then any Harm Touch could ever do.<br>
<br>
And I raise my Lance to you all, and say that &quot;I HAVE CONQURED AND DEFEATED LOVE!&quot;<br>
<br>
Once again. Just as I was as a Child. <br>
Before Genashai.<br>
<br>
Perfect in my True Hatred.<br>
<br>
Just as the Father intended.<br>
<br>
I am a Perfect Child of the Father. He created me, as he did all Tier'dal in a manner that is Perfect. I shall not allow love to stain and make me Imperfect, as it has made others..<br>
<br>
Very ..<br>
<br>
Woodelven like.<br>
<br>
That is all. Take away from this as you wish. <p><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif" WIDTH="127" HEIGHT="110">
"I Know Pain.
I Know Hurt.
I Know Suffering.
I Know Torment.

..And I know how to bring Pain, Hurt, Suffering, and Torment upon your very soul. These are the things that fuel my infinite HATE!"
