er..<br>
<br>
Just don't look at the Bunny Slippers and he will appear to be a strong Knight of Darkness. Didi, The Father created us this way, to be Sinful creatures of Lust, yes. Satisfy yourself if you need be, but Love for the most part will end in you being weaker then you really are. No longer is their any need to care about who's bedding who and who's got who's fiancee tied to some bed wielding a wooden Paddle. Without love, none of that matters.. and thus gives us the ability to focus on things much more Important.<br>
